  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Orb is your fate...</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331910/extras/832ac911af298b73c735946cee2706eb.poster.avif?t=1759581501\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331910/extras/832ac911af298b73c735946cee2706eb.webm?t=1759581501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331910/extras/832ac911af298b73c735946cee2706eb.mp4?t=1759581501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Orb Calls for Two</h2><br>Morkredd is best played as a couch co-op experience. Heed the Orb’s call with a friend or prove your loyalty alone by mastering the unique dual-character controls.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331910/extras/b79bb3983806eec2b03d0f09f945e4e1.poster.avif?t=1759581501\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331910/extras/b79bb3983806eec2b03d0f09f945e4e1.webm?t=1759581501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331910/extras/b79bb3983806eec2b03d0f09f945e4e1.mp4?t=1759581501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your Path is the Orb</h2>You are the Orb’s protector, and the Orb’s light is yours. Survive and master over 60 puzzles while avoiding the shadows caused by your partner and the environment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331910/extras/bce5c561545c34a334ce832c07f00b11.poster.avif?t=1759581501\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331910/extras/bce5c561545c34a334ce832c07f00b11.webm?t=1759581501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331910/extras/bce5c561545c34a334ce832c07f00b11.mp4?t=1759581501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Orb is Your Only Friend</h2><br>An endless abyss of deadly shadows conceal dangers in this cold, dark world. Stay with the Orb if you want to stay alive. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331910/extras/c213d442f893e9cf0b53c39013d1b15b.poster.avif?t=1759581501\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331910/extras/c213d442f893e9cf0b53c39013d1b15b.webm?t=1759581501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331910/extras/c213d442f893e9cf0b53c39013d1b15b.mp4?t=1759581501\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gaze into the Orb</h2><br>Discover ancient secrets about the Orb hidden in the darkness.",
